  "title": "Chemical Technician / Process Technician - Pharma MNC #HMS",
  "description": "<p><strong>Chemical Technician / Process Technician - Pharma MNC </strong><br /><strong>Tuas (pick at at jurong east/ cck) </strong><br /><strong>Contract:</strong> 1-Year<br /><strong>Shift:</strong> <strong>12-hour rotating Day & Night</strong><br /><br /> <strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Operate & monitor production equipment (reactions, distillation, transfers)</p></li><li><p>Load raw materials & solvents into production equipment</p></li><li><p>Monitor process parameters via <strong>DCS, alarms & control panels</strong></p></li><li><p>Perform liquid transfers (truck ↔ storage tanks)</p></li><li><p>Ensure accurate <strong>GMP documentation & batch records</strong></p></li><li><p>Coordinate with Shift Manager, Production Support & Warehouse</p></li><li><p>Perform housekeeping & maintain safety standards</p></li><li><p>Report equipment or process anomalies promptly</p></li><li><p>Support continuous improvement & lean manufacturing initiatives</p></li></ul><p>Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p></p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R1331820</p><p></p>",
